highlights.description: Sal says "I know how you guys feel" as the participants share stories of losing a family member.
Throughout Sal's story, participants express empathy through their acknowledgement responses.
Andrew shares his own story of losing a grandparent.
The discussion of aging grandparents and parents prompts a reflection on independence and the loss of caregivers.
Sal and Gregory share similar experiences with Access-A-Ride being inadequate as a regular mode of transportation.
